    <entry>
      <title>MarkDown_Basic01</title>
      <link href="/2022/10/08/MarkDown_Basic01/"/>
      <url>/2022/10/08/MarkDown_Basic01/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<font size="6"><b>This is a series of codes for learning MarkDown Grammar.</b></font><h2 id="Title-Grammar"><a href="#Title-Grammar" class="headerlink" title="Title Grammar"></a><strong>Title Grammar</strong></h2><h2 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a><strong>标题</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># Level 1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## Level 2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### Level 3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#### Level 4</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">##### Level 5</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">###### Level 6</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Paragapha-Grammar"><a href="#Paragapha-Grammar" class="headerlink" title="Paragapha Grammar"></a><strong>Paragapha Grammar</strong></h2><h2 id="段落"><a href="#段落" class="headerlink" title="段落"></a><strong>段落</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Don&#x27;t put tabs or spaces in front of your  paragraphs.  </span><br><span class="line">Keep lines left-aligned like this.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Don’t put tabs or spaces in front of your  paragraphs.<br>Keep lines left-aligned like this.</p><h2 id="Line-Break"><a href="#Line-Break" class="headerlink" title="Line Break"></a><strong>Line Break</strong></h2><h2 id="换行"><a href="#换行" class="headerlink" title="换行"></a><strong>换行</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">This is the first line.  </span><br><span class="line">句尾添加两个空格加回车即可进行换行  </span><br><span class="line">And this the second line.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>This is the first line.<br>句尾添加两个空格加回车即可进行换行<br>And this the second line.</p><h2 id="Bold-amp-amp-Italic"><a href="#Bold-amp-amp-Italic" class="headerlink" title="Bold &amp;&amp; Italic"></a><strong>Bold &amp;&amp; Italic</strong></h2><h2 id="粗体-斜体"><a href="#粗体-斜体" class="headerlink" title="粗体 斜体"></a><strong>粗体</strong> <em>斜体</em></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">This is <span class="strong">**Bold**</span> <span class="emphasis">*Italic*</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*BlodItalic*</span>**</span>.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>This is <strong><em>Bold Italic</em></strong> &amp;&amp; <strong><em>BlodItalic</em></strong>.</p><h2 id="引用块语法"><a href="#引用块语法" class="headerlink" title="引用块语法"></a><strong>引用块语法</strong></h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">**The quarterly results look great!**</span>  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> Revenue was off the chart.  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> Profits were higher than ever.  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*Everything*</span> is going according to <span class="strong">**plan**</span>.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p> <strong>The quarterly results look great!</strong></p><ul><li>Revenue was off the chart.</li><li><p>Profits were higher than ever.</p><p><em>Everything</em> is going according to <strong>plan</strong>.</p></li></ul></blockquote><h2 id="列表语法（有序列表和无序列表）"><a href="#列表语法（有序列表和无序列表）" class="headerlink" title="列表语法（有序列表和无序列表）"></a><strong>列表语法（有序列表和无序列表）</strong></h2><h3 id="有序列表"><a href="#有序列表" class="headerlink" title="有序列表"></a><strong>有序列表</strong></h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> first item  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> second item  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    Paragapha insert</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    - 引用块  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">3. third item</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>first item  </li><li>second item<br> Paragapha insert<blockquote><p>引用块  </p></blockquote></li><li>third item</li></ol><h3 id="无序列表"><a href="#无序列表" class="headerlink" title="无序列表"></a><strong>无序列表</strong></h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> first item(insert code block)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">        &lt;html&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">        &lt;head&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">            &lt;title&gt;Test&lt;/title&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">        &lt;/head&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> second item(insert image block)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    ![image,famer](./MarkDownLearning/farmer.png)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> third item(insert list block)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> first block</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> second</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> third</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>first item(insert code block)</p>  <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;html&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;head&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;title&gt;Test&lt;/title&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/head&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>second item(insert image block)</p><p>  <img src="/2022/10/08/MarkDown_Basic01/farmer.png" alt="image,famer"></p></li><li><p>third item(insert list block)</p><ul><li>first block</li><li>second</li><li>third</li></ul></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> MarkDown </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
